{"tid":309412,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有片] 廢柴老豆:「有樓留給你也未必是好事」","createTime":"2017-07-05T04:13:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-26T14:04:44.000Z","uid":42188,"like":9,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1adae4701a786f5739d82105ea29f8589b263b8e","tid":309412,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T04:13:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/05/120944_7434dea2450ece4cc48593ed0e1b9460.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F05%2F120944_7434dea2450ece4cc48593ed0e1b9460.jpg&h=9964810b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n賣樓後的九年來一直租住單位至今，馬先生期間曾試過抽居屋卻落空，三年前樓價瘋癲時亦曾遇上業主加租兩成被迫遷，年紀細細的八歲兒子目睹也不禁問「如果我哋當年無賣層樓應該會幾好」父親只好向他詳細解釋，再補加一句勵志明言「<span style=\"color: red;\">如你日後有能力，你也可以自己賺錢買，爸爸未必有能力幫你置業，有樓留給你也未必是好事，自己要努力！</span>」。 <br />\n<br />\n談及現時發展商不斷推出的新樓的劏房單位，馬先生認為不切實際：「二百呎究竟點一家人一起生活，我睇新聞見到好多人死慳死底，要家人協助上會比首期，死慳死底去供款，每日消費五十蚊，交通、食飯甚至連日用品每一樣都要慳住用，究竟係咪好事？！每日返工十幾二十個鐘，無基本消費娛樂，倘若日後樓市逆轉會點？！」 <br />\n<br />\n他認為不會刻意去追價入市，<span style=\"color: red;\">買不起物業也能夠生活，最重要心態自行調節，有地方可讓家人安頓下來，日常生活沒有影響便可。 </span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/nextplus/時事要聞/article/20170228/2_482703_0/-有樓有高潮-落錯車-八歲兒質問父-如果無賣樓我哋會幾好\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnextplus%2F%E6%99%82%E4%BA%8B%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20170228%2F2_482703_0%2F-%E6%9C%89%E6%A8%93%E6%9C%89%E9%AB%98%E6%BD%AE-%E8%90%BD%E9%8C%AF%E8%BB%8A-%E5%85%AB%E6%AD%B2%E5%85%92%E8%B3%AA%E5%95%8F%E7%88%B6-%E5%A6%82%E6%9E%9C%E7%84%A1%E8%B3%A3%E6%A8%93%E6%88%91%E5%93%8B%E6%9C%83%E5%B9%BE%E5%A5%BD&d=%2F%2FQmoH%2FgMcs2fxRgan34XviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=d35c03e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnextplus%2F%E6%99%82%E4%BA%8B%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20170228%2F2_482703_0%2F-%E6%9C%89%E6%A8%93%E6%9C%89%E9%AB%98%E6%BD%AE-%E8%90%BD%E9%8C%AF%E8%BB%8A-%E5%85%AB%E6%AD%B2%E5%85%92%E8%B3%AA%E5%95%8F%E7%88%B6-%E5%A6%82%E6%9E%9C%E7%84%A1%E8%B3%A3%E6%A8%93%E6%88%91%E5%93%8B%E6%9C%83%E5%B9%BE%E5%A5%BD&h=30dcb3e9\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/nextplus/時事要聞/article/20170228/2_482703_0/-有樓有高潮-落錯車-八歲兒質問父-如果無賣樓我哋會幾好</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">成地精</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db902b3cdbca6d8d9b6390a40578c3fa54069791","tid":309412,"uid":48579,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T04:15:41.000Z","msg":"有樓未必係好事<br />\n但無就一定係壞事囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e6aa681c380153ac2c5464aebe5ad85b5ff98ea","tid":309412,"uid":42188,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T04:17:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有樓未必係好事<br />\n但無就一定係壞事囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔知佢個仔10年後睇返段片，會唔會想打柒個老豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e1502c7ed2aa3a258d11c9a0541c0e9ad3bcf3a","tid":309412,"uid":36551,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T04:23:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/05/122145_85b5eb872b5877cc895fb022e6a37087.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F05%2F122145_85b5eb872b5877cc895fb022e6a37087.JPG&h=62c382d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「如果冇能力就冇得講，但如果係有能力，供書教學外，一定要幫忙（子女）...叫佢哋自己買樓結婚，我諗佢哋都唔使結嘞啩，嘿嘿。」針織公司南旋控股主席王庭聰是名副其實的廿四孝父親，在三名子女組織小家庭時贈樓作賀禮；都是土地不足的問題，令香港樓價高得離奇，王庭聰坦言，年輕人大學畢業後，月入也只萬多兩萬，除卻家人幫忙，幾乎「冇乜可能」買樓，「如果父母有能力，我覺得係應該（幫忙）」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170618/56842316\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170618%2F56842316&d=%2F%2FQmoH%2FgMcs2fxRgan34XviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=419c33d8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170618%2F56842316&h=596d3448\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170618/56842316</a>"},{"pid":"500c2f8a8e3624dd2d39bae3c523eaae828aa16a","tid":309412,"uid":26451,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T04:26:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5493694031718f77a1e122d96411ddefd70113c2","tid":309412,"uid":22675,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T04:28:11.000Z","msg":"身邊都有人早幾年見升都放左層樓出去<br />\n諗住等跌果陣再買過<br />\n點知又係租到而家"},{"pid":"7075e059e63b9ec359ad4c29a515436637ccff1d","tid":309412,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T04:40:26.000Z","msg":"八歲就識講呢啲野，好恐怖"},{"pid":"5195f8e81c136c63387c3e589a4f905ff8a80f6f","tid":309412,"uid":40932,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T04:45:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>八歲就識講呢啲野，好恐怖</blockquote><br />\n有幾奇<br />\n小學d同學問住邊已經有對比"},{"pid":"ae8af362451efb94afbe0e63539826464690d19e","tid":309412,"uid":48958,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T04:46:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>八歲就識講呢啲野，好恐怖</blockquote><br />\n有幾奇<br />\n小學d同學問住邊已經有對比</blockquote><br />\n真係唔敢生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a6e4dcbe5d5c91060a0143351db5c30f9e39545","tid":309412,"uid":10503,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T04:48:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>八歲就識講呢啲野，好恐怖</blockquote><br />\n有幾奇<br />\n小學d同學問住邊已經有對比</blockquote><br />\n真係唔敢生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n窮撚就咪學人生仔啦"},{"pid":"d92423654abe2e14775ce16ab4e3c31360a40c61","tid":309412,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T04:48:21.000Z","msg":"又回帶<img