先叫炒，自住都想炒，死硬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df7d8c148d318391484a3890f69b02491f2dc844","tid":309412,"uid":82006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T07:54:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/05/122145_85b5eb872b5877cc895fb022e6a37087.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F05%2F122145_85b5eb872b5877cc895fb022e6a37087.JPG&h=62c382d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「如果冇能力就冇得講，但如果係有能力，供書教學外，一定要幫忙（子女）...叫佢哋自己買樓結婚，我諗佢哋都唔使結嘞啩，嘿嘿。」針織公司南旋控股主席王庭聰是名副其實的廿四孝父親，在三名子女組織小家庭時贈樓作賀禮；都是土地不足的問題，令香港樓價高得離奇，王庭聰坦言，年輕人大學畢業後，月入也只萬多兩萬，除卻家人幫忙，幾乎「冇乜可能」買樓，「如果父母有能力，我覺得係應該（幫忙）」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170618/56842316\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170618%2F56842316&d=%2F%2FQmoH%2FgMcs2fxRgan34XviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=419c33d8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170618%2F56842316&h=596d3448\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170618/56842316</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n終於有d無咁離地既有錢佬講野<br />\n果d乜鳩買少部電話去少次旅行就買到樓果d真係on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42abdc392de4acf58b7c18b55a595886cda43a8b","tid":309412,"uid":93904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T08:28:56.000Z","msg":"有樓留給你也未必是好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25be54c764db9229c05cbbf6e64e24891923086c","tid":309412,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T08:35:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有樓留給你也未必是好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好想知佢d同事朋友見到個訪問會點樣背後笑鳩佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56d8cec350c9a18